Each of the Programs above may result in recommendations ranging from capital improvements to routine maintenance of the plant.  Service Calls are established in parallel to identified needs.  Current planned changes to improve safety include recommendations from the PHA update on 1/4/2013, which the Oxnard Fire/CUPA attended.  WPS/Commercial Cooler has prepared a written schedule of the recommendations which are expected to be completed by 3/29/2013.
